    <body>
      <section eId="sec_21_E">
        <num>21-E</num>
        <heading>Powers of the commissioner to prepare and issue a notice to be posted at worksite</heading>
        <subsection eId="sec_21_E__subsec_a">
          <num>(a)</num>
          <content>
            <p>The duties of employers with regard to the rights of employees to\nthe receipt and payment of wages;\n</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
        <subsection eId="sec_21_E__subsec_b">
          <num>(b)</num>
          <content>
            <p>A toll free number at the department to which employees may direct\nquestions or register complaints concerning an employer's failure to pay\nwages or the conditions of employment; and\n</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
        <subsection eId="sec_21_E__subsec_c">
          <num>(c)</num>
          <content>
            <p>The address of the regional department to file a complaint.\n  2. The notice required pursuant to subdivision one of this section\nshall be distributed to employers in the apparel and garment industries\nto be posted in a visible and prominent location within the worksite.\n</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
      </section>
